{"tid":985608,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇官制撚","createTime":"2019-01-17T17:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T02:28:07.000Z","uid":201356,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d7819cfebf40fa910791655f0c858d648778e7e2","tid":985608,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:50:14.000Z","msg":"有冇熟中國/某地官制or政治制度撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近小弟睇咗本《唐代高層文官》，好迷官制<br />\n越讀越發覺涉及嘅嘢好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔單止地緣、政局事件、傳統，甚至連上古神話都牽涉埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想搵下有冇啲志同道合嘅朋友仔一齊交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411b9fd6815332d0164c06b9e8959cbcfe822fe4","tid":985608,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:35:45.000Z","msg":"bump"},{"pid":"ec0542952e3740ea9864b5fe91efdf805dc83717","tid":985608,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"有啊 常常和習總吃飯 操逼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  反正有百姓養我們 太爽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15241f784b72750a97c8293176f2f0a5e605d0bb","tid":985608,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:58:16.000Z","msg":"bump"},{"pid":"1dea995ad89563723b20f8ccc65626d1a799d86d","tid":985608,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"bump bump"},{"pid":"61f920696c18e32a2f241d268bdf7f539122b353","tid":985608,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"ao eo aco ca"},{"pid":"6c002529d5c60041b054d92310d9d8834fa07adc","tid":985608,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:32:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db055c354afb122141ad9897b80134a4c643dada","tid":985608,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"試簡述官，職，差遣（20分）"},{"pid":"19d3a7e9b3e013b33a5ce46d704f8d5e682b33a4","tid":985608,"uid":201356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"db055c354afb122141ad9897b80134a4c643dada","tid":985608,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"試簡述官，職，差遣（20分）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T13:11:39.000Z","msg":"唔記得咗lu <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  利申中史DSEer<br />\n<br />\n官喺宋代context摷返出嚟綜合下，就係階官、寄祿官。宋朝嘅官咪係唐朝三省六部廢弛咗之後用嚟定待遇、等級同pay grade嘅官名，升遷考核都按佢<br />\n<br />\n職又叫貼職，就係一啲乜乜勿勿頭銜攞嚟表示佢額外加咗人工、返工排隊又可以排前啲。文官就係啲乜乜殿乜乜閣，武官(使臣)就係啲乜乜使 (都係啲宮廷部門嘢嚟)<br />\n<br />\n差遣又叫使職、職事官就係佢個崗位，上至宰相執政官、中至各種侍從官、宣差、監司、下至各種專知、厘務官呢啲雜流甚至大頭兵都係差遣，見親啲知同知判通判管勾勾當干辦主管提舉提轄提點提調乜乜公務乜乜使基本都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91cf4e12378ce9cdc4e0800a977f1071b6ce5d7","tid":985608,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"bump"},{"pid":"83fffe084c9811b0db2c49068452ac3a833622d3","tid":985608,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:28:07.000Z","msg":"bump"}]}